title: A Plethora of Twinkies Abound

MAS_UTrack_V003
A Plethora Of Twinkies Abound!
By: Killer Fish (Todd Showalter)
of Late Nite Software Labs   --------------------------------
Written on or about Feb/94   (c)
Written on UltraTracker v1.5, this happy little ditty is a    celebration of all which is not calculus mid-terms.  Enjoy it   in the light, fluffy, unassuming way that it was intended.
